# The upstream versions Gancho currently builds against — the single source
# the upstream canary (scripts/check-upstream-deps.sh) compares against each
# week. Update a pin ONLY as part of the dependency-update PR that adopts the
# new version (docs/DEPENDENCIES.md has the per-dependency runbook).
#
# Cross-checked pins (the canary fails if these drift from the repo):
#   SPARKLE   ↔ scripts/fetch-sparkle.sh SPARKLE_VERSION
#   SAUCE     ↔ Packages/GanchoKit/Package.resolved
#   SQLCIPHER ↔ Packages/GanchoKit/Package.resolved (sqlcipher.swift, pulled
#               in by the GRDB fork). GRDB tracks the UPSTREAM groue tag the
#               fork branch is based on; KEYBOARDSHORTCUTS is maintained by
#               hand (its resolved file is generated, not tracked).
GRDB=7.11.0
SQLCIPHER=4.16.0
SPARKLE=2.9.4
SAUCE=2.5.1
KEYBOARDSHORTCUTS=2.4.0
